  Alright, I think this is what you all have been waiting for! If not, go suck
  on something, because this  game rocks and  you should have been waiting for
  it.

  It's here at last.  The PUBLIC SERVER PATCH for Battlefield 2, the best game
  of 2005. So, a few things about how this  works:  This WILL NOT ALLOW YOU TO
  PLAY ON LEGIT UNCRACKED  SERVERS.  If someone wants to do that, go ahead. We
  do not want to, and will not, make a patch for that.  Buy the game (we are). 
  So, what is a public server patch you ask?  It means that when the SERVER is
  running this patch, their  server will still show  up in the in-game server,
  but WILL NOT AUTHENTICATE CD KEYS (aka all you poor ass mofo's out there can
  play multiplayer with  your crax0red copies).  The server won't authenticate
  against  the master server,  but it WILL CHECK AGAINST ITS OWN CD-KEYS (aka,
  two people with the same key on one server), so USE THE KEYGEN for your key.

  Thank you to the lovely RELOADED for saying that groups could use their fine
  crack to make a server patch, but low and behold, it was all for not. We did
  not need/use their crack at all for this - this is just the dedicated server
  file cracked (which WE cracked, NOT Reloaded).  Nonetheless, great job guys,
  and we all appreciate what you do.  Still, buy this one game. It's worth it.
  The only reason we cracked  this  was because  we wanted to play multiplayer
  for the  next two days until the game hits the shelves. EA, we're very sorry
  but we couldn't wait. We really wanted to play.  Please don't sue us?  kthx.

  THIS IS ONLY A PATCHED DEDICATED SERVER EXECUTABLE.  Anyone who tries to run
  the server from GUI is a tard anyway.  Don't be doing that, your server will
  suck.

  Now, we tested this with  both the  RELOADED copy.  The clone may or may not
  work - we're pretty sure it will  because we  tested this with a pure server
  and the RELOADED worked, so that'd suggest the  clone would work too. Still,
  if it doesn't, not our fault, and we don't really care.

  We didn't hit that PunkBuster issue, but if you have PunkBuster disabled, be
  sure to disable when you're looking through the server  list or else it will
  filter out your server and you'll think it's not working and come yapping to
  people complaining,  but it will really just be you being an idiot.  We WERE
  able to use PunkBuster on our server while using this patch, and did not hit
  any crashes whatsoever. Don't be an idiot. This patch works.

  THIS  SHOULD ALLOW LEGITIMITE PLAYERS TO PLAY ON THE SERVERS ALSO.  AKA - IF
  YOU BUY THIS GAME AND HAVE A LEGIT CD-KEY YOU CAN STILL PLAY.

  Enjoy!

